markets.title: Will Keir Starmer say Trump at 2pm EST press conference with Trump?
markets.rules_primary: If Keir Starmer says Trump as part of 2pm EST press conference with Trump, then the market resolves to Yes.
markets.rules_secondary: Video of 2pm EST press conference with Trump will be primarily used to resolve the market; if a consensus by Kalshi employees cannot be reached using video, transcripts of 2pm EST press conference with Trump will be used according to the news publications listed in the contract. Hyphenated or compound words used with <word> will not be included.
markets.early_close_condition: This market will close and expire early if the event occurs.
